<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>102</hymn_number>
<author>Donnie Sax Sanders &amp; the Loud Cry Revival</author>
<title>Yesu Kristi, Mai Cetona LW102</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Yesu Kristi, Mai Cetona
 Ɗan Allah Mai Tsarki ne.
 Halleluya, halleluya.

[V2]
 2) Ina shaidar suna naka,
 Sunanka mai daraja.
 Halleluya, halleluya.

[V3]
 3) Ina girmama sunanka,
 Ubangiji Mai Ceto. Halleluya, halleluya.

[V4]
 4) Jinin Yesu ne ya zama
 Fansar masu zunubi.
 Halleluya, halleluya.

[V5]
 5) Ina ɗaukaka sunanka,
 Yesu, kai mai ba da rai.
 Halleluya, halleluya.

[V6]
 6) I, zan shaida sunan Yesu
 Har ma duniya duk ta ji.
 Halleluya, halleluya.

[V7]
 7) Allah ya yi ƙaunar duniya,
 Ƙaunarsa mai girma kuwa.
 Halleluya, halleluya.

[V8]
 8) Ni na gaskata da Yesu
 Ɗan Allah Mai Tsarki ne.
 Halleluya, halleluya.</lyrics>
</song>